# gallica app
## Requirement 
- Nvidia GPU
  Nvidia Container Toolkit : https://docs.nvidia.com/datacenter/cloud-native/container-toolkit/latest/install-guide.html

- Docker: https://docs.docker.com/get-docker
  Docker supported GPU : https://docs.docker.com/config/containers/resource_constraints/#gpu



# Docker Tutorial https://docs.docker.com/get-started/
# COMMAND TO RUN :
# building image
docker-compose build
# start container
docker compose up
# Specific container in docker compose
docker-compose up -d image container_name
# Gradio App launched at http://localhost:7860/
# Stop containers
docker-compose down
# Running containers 
docker-compose ps
# Remove every data system, can be replaced by image, colume, network : Warning it may erase everything (inn Windows that doesn't work at all ;) ) 
docker system prune 
